:HELP NAME=OMH006GEN.Answer Maintenance - Help
:XH3.Answer Maintenance
:ISCH ROOTS='answer maintenance'.
Answer Maintenance

:P.
The answer maintenance function enables you to maintain the answers
to the questions you have previously created. You can create as
many answers as you like and use only a subset when the question
is connected to a question list.

:P.
Please consult the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP OMH00602IX'.
Q&A concepts
:ELINK.
for more information about answers.
