:XH3.Option
:P.
These are the list options. The options all act on a
specific list entry. The following options are available;

:PARML.
:PT.2=Change
:PD.
Use this option to change the answer.
:PT.4=Delete
:PD.
Use this option to remove the answer. You cannot remove
an answer if it is used to answer a question.
:EPARML.
